title: 8/15 move, very big and sunny 3BR/1bth nr Broadway/14th St and ferry
posting_body: ['https://youtu.be/u6Gct0DslD0', 'This is the YouTube tour of the apartment.', ' Please note, apartments tend to look smaller on videos than they actually are.', '*10 min walk from NW Broadway, 5 min from ferry', '*2nd floor, top floor', '*Sizable bedrooms, one of them would fit king, other two would fit Queen or full', '*All hardwood floor', '*Very sunny', '*Laundry, supermarket nearby', '*BQE right nearby for drivers', '*8/1 move', '*Pets case by case', '* Guarantor or Insurent accepted', "Please email with your name, phone number (required - we won't contact you back without this), tell us a little bit about you and whoever you'll be living with and the best time to view or if you're out of town and cannot be present, request zoom or video tour.", 'BROKER FEE APPLIES!']
